            "title": "QXO announces common stock offering",
            "description": "<html><body><ul> <li>QXO (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QXO\" title=\"QXO, Inc.\">QXO</a></span>) on Wednesday said it intends to make an offering of $500 million of shares of its common stock.</li>\n<li>QXO’s common stock is listed on the New York Stock Exchange under the symbol “QXO.”</li> <li>QXO intends to use the net proceeds from the offering to finance a portion of the consideration for the pending acquisition of Beacon Roofing Supply.</li> <li>QXO  <font color=\"red\">-1.96%</font> after hours to  $13.98.</li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20069930-qxo-announces-common-stock-offering\">Press Release</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>",
